'''Nixor [[Spaceport/Legends|Spaceport]]''' [[Orbit/Legends|orbited]] around the [[Nixor system/Legends|Nixor system]] around the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It was most commonly described as a disorganized mess due to the longstanding feud between the [[Nixor (species)|Nixors]] and the rest of the system. Due to their stubborn attitude, the Nixors refused to upgrade the spaceport as necessary or even give it the most basic of repairs. Due to its location, it was always crowded, which caused many pilots to avoid it.

However, this was to the advantage of [[Ferus Olin]] and [[Roan Lands]]. The two chose this as one of many places where they could meet each other in secret, and it was here that the two met up once again. Roan met with Ferus to provide him with the necessary prefab shelters, food, and medical supplies in order to set up an [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] sanctuary for survivors of the [[Great Jedi Purge/Legends|Great Jedi Purge]].

